{"tid":2229338,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Airbnb萬聖節禁訂一晚房 防開派對爆疫","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T10:14:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"677afddbeda90a03e62b4218dec599ae8740175f","tid":2229338,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201004/TQJYYW2OJ5GFNJF2JPKC25J4QY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201004%2FTQJYYW2OJ5GFNJF2JPKC25J4QY%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil0wAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=7198cbb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201004%2FTQJYYW2OJ5GFNJF2JPKC25J4QY%2F&h=8941b91e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201004/TQJYYW2OJ5GFNJF2JPKC25J4QY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nAirbnb萬聖節禁訂一晚房 防開派對爆疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d_cRrh1j0indrbJFmpNI3b17FGE=/1769x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJPGHWLWBJCIDDVJNJ7KF4TVEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fd_cRrh1j0indrbJFmpNI3b17FGE%3D%2F1769x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJPGHWLWBJCIDDVJNJ7KF4TVEA.jpg&h=7ca10e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Airbnb宣佈限制美加用戶在萬聖節訂房。<br />\n<br />\n網上訂房平台Airbnb前日宣佈，將於本月底萬聖節期間禁止一晚的房間出租，以防有人租房舉行大型派對。發言人指措施是為了在武漢肺炎疫情下「在關鍵時刻盡本份在北美協助保障公眾健康」。<br />\n<br />\nAirbnb宣佈將於本月30日至31日，在美國和加拿大禁止用戶租用整個住宅單位，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年曾釀五死槍擊案<br />\n<br />\n去年加州奧林達市有人在平台上租用房間舉辦未經許可的萬聖節派對，終釀成槍擊案，五人死亡。。。。。。。。。。。。，並把處所使用者限制在16人以下。平台警告會向違例者採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/英國廣播公司"}]}